'''''Move It or Lose It''''' is an online document informing ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'' players about the so-called House Pack-Up operation. It consists of a game-related F.A.Q. and a short [[in-universe]] narrative, primarily having the form of a conversation between [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Braedic Ekirk]] and an unnamed [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Admiral/Legends|admiral]] who are devising a plan to demolish abandoned buildings around the galaxy. Although short, the story introduces two characters and three organizations.

==Dramatis personae==
*[[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] {{Mo}}
*[[Braedic Ekirk]] {{1st}}
*Unnamed [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] admiral {{1st}}

